docs.snippet: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., Feb. 13 (UPI) -- Fay Crocket shot a three-over-par 74 today in winds so strong they rolled golf balls across the greens. The round lifted her into a tie with Jo Ann Prentice for the lead in the St. Petersburg women's open.
